title: Australia’s Home-Price Gains Cool With RBA Pivot Denting Outlook
description: Australia’s home-price growth decelerated in December and the two biggest markets edged lower, as the risk of renewed interest-rate hikes weighed on both sentiment and the outlook for property in the year ahead.
